title: Renotify Pro v2.0.5 APK (Android)
description:
ReNotify+ Speed Notification Maker!

ReNotify+ is an enhanced version of the popular app ReNotify. It includes all the existing features, plus a history of the last 20 notifications made, the ability to edit notifications, and expandable notifications for Jelly Bean users.

ReNotify+ has a clean and simple UI, is free from ads, and takes up virtually no memory.

If you have any issues or suggestions, leave a comment or email me at the address below. If the translation is wrong, you can help fix it by sending me a correction!

Keywords: Notification, notifications, notification maker, speed notification maker, quick notification maker, fast notification maker.

What's in this version : (Updated : 23 March 2016)
Version 2.0.5
- Fixed Portuguese translation
Please note that you may need to open the app to restore your notifications if they don't restore automatically.
Required Android O/S : 4.1+
